<para> The Multi-Tier JDBC driver for Informix consists of a set of generic JDBC client classes and the Informix Database agent on the server utilizing the built in database independent network layer for communication between the client and server.</para><para>The <ulink url="OpenLink">OpenLink</ulink>  Multi-Tier Drivers for Informix are a Type A class driver developed using the ESQL/C call level interface.</para><para>These drivers are currently available for Informix versions 7.x, 9.x(IDS 2000) and beyond.</para><para>  [[/images/aodbcst.gif|]]</para><para> /Informix Multi-Tier JDBC Driver Architecture Diagram Image scaled down; Click to enlarge./</para><para> This driver is available for Windows, Linux, Unix(most flavours), Mac Classic, Mac OS X or any Java enabled Operating systems.</para><para> </para></section></docbook>